name: $unknown
desc: The source human does not know the value.

name: $asked
desc: There is reason to expect (from the workflow) that the value may become known.

name: $temp
desc: The workflow didn't lead to this value being known.

name: $not-asked
desc: The information is not available due to security, privacy or related reasons.

name: $masked
desc: The source system wasn't capable of supporting this element.

name: $unsupported
desc: The content of the data is represented in the resource narrative.

name: $astext
desc: Some system or workflow process error means that the information is not available.

name: $error
desc: The value is not available because the observation procedure (test, etc.) was not performed.
